# Environment Variables

Copy this to `.env.local` and fill in your values:

```env
# API Configuration
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api

# Environment
VITE_ENV=development

# Feature Flags (optional)
VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=false
VITE_ENABLE_DEBUG_MODE=true
```

## Available Variables

| Variable | Purpose | Example |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `VITE_API_BASE_URL` | Backend API endpoint | `http://localhost:3000/api` |
| `VITE_ENV` | Environment mode | `development`, `production` |
| `VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS` | Enable analytics tracking | `true` or `false` |
| `VITE_ENABLE_DEBUG_MODE` | Enable debug logging | `true` or `false` |

## Usage

Access in code:

```typescript
const apiUrl = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE_URL;
const isDevelopment = import.meta.env.VITE_ENV === 'development';
```

## Production Build

Create `.env.production.local`:

```env
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.kartzia-eeden.com
VITE_ENV=production
VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=true
VITE_ENABLE_DEBUG_MODE=false
```
